### US-001 – User Authentication
**As a** user,
**I want to** be able to log in with my email and password,
**So that** I can access my private dashboard.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- GIVEN I am on the login page
- WHEN I enter a valid email and password
- THEN I should be redirected to my dashboard

- **Priority**: P0
- **Criticality**: Critical
- **Status**: Ready
- **UI Test Status**: Pending

**UI Test Workflow:**
```json
{
  "user_story_id": "US-001",
  "criticality": "Critical",
  "environment": "staging",
  "test_name": "User Login Authentication",
  "description": "Validates user can log in with valid credentials",
  "preconditions": [
    "User account exists in staging database",
    "Login page is accessible"
  ],
  "steps": [
    {
      "step_number": 1,
      "action": "navigate",
      "target": "https://staging.yourapp.com/login",
      "description": "Navigate to login page",
      "expected_result": "Login form is displayed"
    },
    {
      "step_number": 2,
      "action": "fill",
      "target": "#email",
      "value": "test@example.com",
      "description": "Enter valid email",
      "expected_result": "Email field accepts input"
    },
    {
      "step_number": 3,
      "action": "fill",
      "target": "#password",
      "value": "validpassword123",
      "description": "Enter valid password",
      "expected_result": "Password field accepts input"
    },
    {
      "step_number": 4,
      "action": "click",
      "target": "[data-testid='login-button']",
      "description": "Click login button",
      "expected_result": "Login process initiates"
    },
    {
      "step_number": 5,
      "action": "wait",
      "target": ".dashboard",
      "description": "Wait for dashboard to load",
      "expected_result": "Dashboard page loads"
    },
    {
      "step_number": 6,
      "action": "assert",
      "target": ".user-welcome",
      "value": "Welcome",
      "description": "Verify welcome message appears",
      "expected_result": "User sees welcome message"
    }
  ],
  "cleanup_steps": [
    {
      "action": "logout",
      "description": "Log out user to clean session"
    }
  ],
  "success_criteria": [
    "User successfully logs in with valid credentials",
    "User is redirected to dashboard",
    "Welcome message is displayed"
  ]
}
```

